#: of numpy.astype:17
msgid ""
"Specifies whether to copy an array when the specified dtype matches the data "
"type of the input array ``x``. If ``True``, a newly allocated array must "
"always be returned. If ``False`` and the specified dtype matches the data "
"type of the input array, the input array must be returned; otherwise, a "
"newly allocated array must be returned. Defaults to ``True``."
msgstr ""

